                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/press/news/2010/bachelet_chief.html?id=614312" title="">
                        Norway congratulates new UN head of gender equality
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 15.09.2010]</p>
                <p>Norway congratulates Chile’s former President Michelle Bachelet on her appointment as head of the UN’s new entity for gender equality and the empowerment of women (UN Women).   </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp1715857533_wp1367756802_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl00_Label1"></span>                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/aktuelt/taler_artikler/ministeren/taler-og-artikler-av-barne--likestilling/2010/Global-Roundtable-on-Board-Diversity.html?id=599588" title="">
                        Global Roundtable on Board Diversity
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">An overview of the Gender quotation on company boards in Norway</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion, 30.03.2010]</p>
                <p>Speach held 26th of March 2010. At International Finance Corporation (IFC), (Verdensbanken), Washington D.C., USA  </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp1715857533_wp1367756802_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl01_Label1"></span>                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/aktuelt/taler_artikler/ministeren/taler-og-artikler-av-barne--likestilling/2010/Adaption-in-working-life-and-equality-for-both-women-and-men.html?id=598260" title="">
                        Adaption in working life and equality for both women and men
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">UN COMMISSION ON THE STATUS OF WOMEN 1 – 12 MARCH 2010</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion, 20.03.2010]</p>
                <p>Seminar hosted by the Norwegian  Consulate in New York, Women`s Forum and Catalyst  The last 40 years has seen substantial equality between the genders come true, with great changes in Norwegian culture, politics and economic life.   Today, we are discussing men’s roles and rights in terms of parental leave, along with promoting women to the upper echelons of economic life.  </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
