        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/aktuelt/taler_artikler/taler_og_artikler_av_ovrig_politisk_lede/statssekretar-gry-larsen/2009/women_peace_security.html?id=591492" title="">
                        Putting policy into practice
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">Conference in Oslo 11.11.2009</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 11.11.2009]</p>
                <p>- For me, women, peace and security is not a gender issue. It is a cross-gender issue. It is a security issue. It is an issue for women and men alike – and an issue of our common interest and future, State Secretary Gry Larsen said in her opening statement at a conference in Oslo on 11.11.09.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
